title: Ciena 5171: CFM Service Status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/ciena
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the operational status of a CFM service, which is either enabled or disabled.
 If the operational status changes from its value at discovery, the check returns {CRIT}.
 Otherwise, it returns {OK}.

 This check supports the Ciena 5171 Packetwave Platform.

 The relevant MIB is CIENA-CES-CFM-MIB.

item:
 The CFM service name as provided by the device.

discovery:
 One service is created for each CFM service name.
